    descriptionEn: "A kind old fisherman frees a magical fish — but when wishes grow greedy, he learns what truly matters.",
    descriptionId: "Nelayan tua yang baik hati membebaskan ikan ajaib — namun ketika permintaan berubah tamak, ia belajar apa yang sungguh berharga.",
    categorySlug: "moral-stories",
    authorSlug: "axto-creative-team",
    coverEmoji: "🐟",
    coverPalette: "ocean",
    ageMin: 4,
